OverHistory.UPDCommentry: A wicket of the first delivery and more importantly it is a dot ball!  Chennai needs 17 runs from 5 balls! WICKET Dwaine Pretorius lbw Jaydev Unadkat (Chennai Super Kings 139 Runs for 7 wickets). Jaydev Unadkat bowling to Dwaine Pretorius, good length ball, pitching on leg stump, Dwaine Pretorius looks to flick this on the leg side but the yorker crashes onto the pads, there is a huge appeal from the Mumbai players but the umpire is unmoved and Rohit takes this upstairs, Ball Tracking shows THREE REDS and Pretorius has to depart.
